Saudi Bourse to Start Integrated ‘Tadawulaty’ Investor Services

-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 
2011-03-12T07:54:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-12/saudi-bourse-to-start-integrated-tadawulaty-investor-services.html
The  Saudi Stock Exchange  will start
integrated services entitled “Tadawulaty” on March 17, the
bourse announced on its website.  The services include consolidated holdings, electronic
voting and dividends reporting, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
 mharoutunian@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
